From 297d1ef48eb80f7c168a155b7bc3e4061a3c5d8c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: ekane bryan <ekanebryan5@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 22 Jul 2026 19:23:52 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(frontend): organizer wallet page + admin payouts
 management

- Organizer Wallet page (/organizer/wallet): balances (available/pending/
  lifetime/paid-out), fee/grace/min rules, request-payout modal (amount +
  mobile money or bank details), payout requests list + cancel, and a
  recent-transactions ledger.
- Admin Payouts page (/admin/payouts): filtered payout table with
  approve/reject/mark-paid actions, summary cards, and an editable
  platform-settings panel (fee %, grace hours, min payout).
- walletService + adminPayoutService API clients, nav links + wallet icon,
  routes, and EN/FR translations (wallet.*, payouts.*, nav.wallet/payouts).
